<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>건의 접수 완료</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/suggest.css">

  <style>
    .success-box {
      width: 60%;
      margin: 60px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 45px 50px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .success-icon {
      font-size: 80px;
      color: #0072ff;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .success-btn {
      margin-top: 25px;
      display: inline-block;
      background: #003c8f;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      color: white;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 17px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .success-btn:hover {
      background: #002d66;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="success-box">
    <div class="success-icon">✔</div>

    <h2>건의가 정상적으로 접수되었습니다.</h2>

    <p style="margin-top: 18px; font-size: 16px; color:#444;">
      전달해주신 내용은 내부에서 검토 후 필요한 경우 반영될 예정입니다.
    </p>

    <a href="/" class="success-btn">메인으로 돌아가기</a>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
